data.title: Fairfax Radiology Center at Woodburn
data.text:
I had a wonderful experience at Fairfax Radiology Center at Woodburn. The staff are very professional. The place is clean and nice. The location is excellent, not crowded, and it is easy to get to it. I highly recommend this location for CT scans.

Happy Patient

A Fine Needle Biopsy is intimidating to any patient. The team at Fairfax Radiology did a great job with humor and quality care!

Happy Patient

Excellent experience. The staff is quick, knowledgeable, and thorough, while still being friendly and compassionate. They specialize in more difficult and detailed scans, which is what I needed. I highly recommend Fairfax Radiology when it comes to more complex needs.

Happy Patient

Professional, caring, extremely competent and friendly. We always feel comfortable and know we are in good hands.

Happy Patient
